<plot>N.C.B.S is about a young girl, named Trisha Authur, telling the story of her father, Ronald Authur, the leader of an elite squad called, N.C.B.S. After suffering a very traumatic injury, Ronald is forced to sit on the sidelines and watch an unqualified man lead his men into certain doom. The stress of watching his men suffer and the memory of the traumatic injury he suffered, is weighing on Ronald and causing stress on his marriage. Ronald must figure out a way to get back into N.C.B.S fast, not only for his men, but for his family as well. Ronald is left with no choice but to overcome his fears and put his life on the line for everybody he loves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?386696</url></doc>
